{"tid":2293231,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得買左隻停牌股生不如死","createTime":"2020-11-20T05:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T06:04:22.000Z","uid":351648,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5745e1003605f8581e538e4b649af81a53654b65","tid":2293231,"uid":351648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T05:59:09.000Z","msg":"早前康宏賣廣告，話公司有打不死嘅精神。<br />\n公司打唔死啫，大佬，我哋小股東嘅資金已經因為停牌鎖住三年，唔係好襟打㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇住康宏兩幫大股東近日鬥法愈演愈烈。當然，兄弟同心，其利斷金係常識。<br />\n但我哋呢啲真&middot;小股東都唔會要求咁高啦，凈係希望你哋拳來拳往，<br />\n都唔好搞到我哋。高抬貴手啦！唔該！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地淨係想復牌同埋唔好FING錢落海啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b57278db8d25b649ef85fec2d9bac4743e145d7","tid":2293231,"uid":357569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:06:21.000Z","msg":"小股東肉隨玷板上=只可以齊齊坐艇<br />\n做得啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc7501c56dd92015d782822870a31f3dcc20b1d","tid":2293231,"uid":351648,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:40:22.000Z","msg":"每次睇到有關佢既新聞就覺得係折磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不吐不快<br />\n作為真正嘅小股東，我哋冇錢請人拉橫額、出宣傳車搞騷。我哋要求唔高，只係拜託啲大股東兩件事：<br />\n<br />\n首先係要集中精力令公司復牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔講之前誰是誰非啦，但依家可唔可以做好復牌先，咪搞咁多大龍鳳得唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小股東唔係一復牌就一定會即時沽晒手頭啲貨，但至緊要係資金可以靈活流動。你哋打交還打交，唔好攬炒，累我哋等多三年啦。你老板!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家係康宏復牌嘅關鍵期，差少少啫。你哋下星期係股東會再打，搞到換晒所有董事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我哋就心臟病發啦。<br />\n有大股東話要換咗成個董事局，咁有乜好計復牌先？唔係諗住整件馬屎坑出嚟講兩嘴就搞得掂啦嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n馬屎坑話佢係「橋樑」，揾鬼信咩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢咁高調，一睇就知係受人錢財、替人消災啫。做戲都揾件好戲啲㗎啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你換晒啲人，管理層梗散，公司梗會半天吊，港交所點會咁傻仔，就咁俾你復牌呀? 咁小股東咪要企晒喺度?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee8821d0d538d10deb80a3e39bf594efaac90f8","tid":2293231,"uid":357569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:07:04.000Z","msg":"呢排真係熱話<br />\n康宏環球雙方過招<br />\n<a href=\"http://today.hkcd.com/content/2020-11/20/content_1230142.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftoday.hkcd.com%2Fcontent%2F2020-11%2F20%2Fcontent_1230142.html&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=2672d4a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://today.hkcd.com/content/2020-11/20/content_1230142.html</a><br />\n樓g摩牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61591ebb862d252dda79db1c9e3de9942a5211a3","tid":2293231,"uid":351648,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:19:03.000Z","msg":"第二，唔好一味向公司興訟，燒晒公司啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你大股東有私己錢提告係你嘅事，但公司與訟就係要用阿公嘅錢，即係我哋股東嘅錢。唔好要我哋埋單得唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋三年前要求更換所有董事，之後告公司，今年已經被法庭判敗訴。玩一次算數啦。但點解仍要上訴，仲要分兩次嚟告康宏呢？告完再告都不特止，另外仲要求法院開庭批出臨時禁制令，等你哋為翻案再買多一重保險。大佬，你唔好咁燒我哋啲錢啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cce8448b21e8546902f79a3e837dd08ce95a3c","tid":2293231,"uid":86449,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:22:35.000Z","msg":"之前買中隻佳兆業, 停牌果排真係日日係咁睇最新發展<br />\n今次康宏又關姓郭果家人事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 無買康宏"},{"pid":"715af86e4492deae1792fd55e3e499b37b26b339","tid":2293231,"uid":351648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e3cce8448b21e8546902f79a3e837dd08ce95a3c","tid":2293231,"uid":86449,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:22:35.000Z","msg":"之前買中隻佳兆業, 停牌果排真係日日係咁睇最新發展<br />\n今次康宏又關姓郭果家人事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 無買康宏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:26:44.000Z","msg":"日日都等緊幾時講復牌 個人都神經質左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7841a919d1057f9911d3c82969efae3fb5cdc8","tid":2293231,"uid":351648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:33:13.000Z","msg":"其實睇返最新嘅官司，係由另一位法官審嘅。今次法官喺判辭話，佢都見到有相當強嘅證據，支持公司話有關股權涉及不當配發股份交易。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁佢都講到好白㗎啦。醒啲啦! 同時，法官又話，咁樣喺上訴開庭前咁短時間內，又另外要求法院出臨時禁制令唔係幾啱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢再話，就算出到俾你，其實對規範主席主持股東會都係作用不大嘅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢只係差啲未講出口：咁係咪濫用咗司法程序呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n從以上看，呢啲訴訟嘅法律理據都好似唔係好實凈，我哋唔明點解仍要不斷興訟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁樣到頭來，究竟係邊個埋單、邊個承擔風險先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個當然唔係收得好貴嘅律師啦，結果咪又係用真金白銀私己錢嘅你老板，同埋公司，即係我哋成班股東埋單囉!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再講一次，唔該各位大股東睇住我哋啲小股東，喺復牌前收手啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算你哋之間係有仇口不共戴天，係都要搞埋下星期個股東會嘅，咁唔該拗埋佢、攞個彩就算啦，就咁落幕，當係了斷啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做大事嘅，要學識放手呢。"},{"pid":"4dca7a1c153795dd91f5719de371df9361079278","tid":2293231,"uid":44884,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:39:41.000Z","msg":"傻仔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你覺得佢地care你地班小股東？<br />\n買得的屎咁多錢就過主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4bf09e2cdfc189d40ec59517f067087add22f46","tid":2293231,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:40:32.000Z","msg":"樓主買左幾大注？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f996c2d1e500161dbfdc52e51a8780f4fd1720","tid":2293231,"uid":357569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dca7a1c153795dd91f5719de371df9361079278","tid":2293231,"uid":44884,"lik