gmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家係康宏復牌嘅關鍵期，差少少啫。你哋下星期係股東會再打，搞到換晒所有董事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我哋就心臟病發啦。<br />\n有大股東話要換咗成個董事局，咁有乜好計復牌先？唔係諗住整件馬屎坑出嚟講兩嘴就搞得掂啦嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n馬屎坑話佢係「橋樑」，揾鬼信咩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢咁高調，一睇就知係受人錢財、替人消災啫。做戲都揾件好戲啲㗎啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你換晒啲人，管理層梗散，公司梗會半天吊，港交所點會咁傻仔，就咁俾你復牌呀? 咁小股東咪要企晒喺度?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小股東唔係一復牌就一定會即時沽晒手頭啲貨，但至緊要係資金可以靈活流動。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你講大話！<br />\n<br />\n你唔沽 點「靈活流動」d錢<br />\n個個都想鬥快靈活流動 你唔沽曬咪輸更多<br />\n<br />\n結論：小股東<del>唔係</del>一復牌就一定會即時沽晒手頭啲貨<br />\n你唔好呃9我喇 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e95317aaf9b4351f9b0a7f9bb0cefd6d87259d6","tid":2293231,"uid":180251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T04:16:34.000Z","msg":"樓主有幾多股？"},{"pid":"1391b78413d6aa23e3886377e40eaec7d16cec97","tid":2293231,"uid":237558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T04:18:28.000Z","msg":"下次買前 問下間公司做咩先。。<br />\n應該做金融既人，都有聽過佢地既「戰績」"},{"pid":"10c101bca91bf910179587e65c3d1d8b85b4dac4","tid":2293231,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:47:54.000Z","msg":"承興苦主路過"},{"pid":"0511d9e278e87e09057ed6aba90f096e151e2c5c","tid":2